sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as LlamaStackDistribution<br/>Reconciler
    participant LLServer as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,LLServer: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (CR created)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service,<br/>SA, PVC, RoleBinding, NetworkPolicy<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Operator->>LLServer: GET /v1/health<br/>HTTP/8321, plaintext, no auth
    LLServer-->>Operator: Health status
    Operator->>LLServer: GET /v1/providers<br/>HTTP/8321, plaintext, no auth
    LLServer-->>Operator: Provider info
    Operator->>LLServer: GET /v1/version<br/>HTTP/8321, plaintext, no auth
    LLServer-->>Operator: Version info
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update CR status subresource<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+

    Note over User,LLServer: Flow 2: ConfigMap Change Detection

    User->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: ConfigMap watch event<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Find referencing LLSDs<br/>(field indexer lookup)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update Deployment annotation<br/>(triggers rolling restart)

    Note over Prometheus,KRBP: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>KRBP: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SAR)
    KRBP->>Operator: Forward to metrics<br/>HTTP/8080, localhost only
    Operator-->>KRBP: Metrics response
    KRBP-->>Prometheus: Metrics response
